19:41.440 --> 19:43.408
How'd you like Gardini Prep?

19:43.450 --> 19:44.872
Oh, it got canceled.

19:44.910 --> 19:47.743
Nova:
Everything shuts down
around here.

19:47.780 --> 19:50.749
Mardi Gras, Super Bowl, rain.
Don't matter.

19:50.790 --> 19:52.985
How'd you know
we were going to visit?

19:53.020 --> 19:54.385
