20:13.910 --> 20:16.538
And you know
we'd have some fun.

20:16.580 --> 20:18.445
- ( both laugh )
- You have your own life, Nova.

20:18.480 --> 20:19.902
You don't need
to be inconvenienced.

20:19.950 --> 20:22.874
How's my nephew
an inconvenience?

20:22.920 --> 20:26.447
