is a lot of responsibility.

20:26.490 --> 20:28.014
I don't need
taking care of.

20:28.060 --> 20:29.379
It's a new city for him--

20:29.420 --> 20:30.853
A city I can show him around.

20:30.890 --> 20:32.585
Micah doesn't need to be
walking around New Orleans--

20:32.630 --> 20:34.222
The spades table is ready.

20:35.900 --> 20:38.619
Now, who want to get
their ass spanked?

20:50.650 --> 20:52.800
Hollywood:
Oh, hell, no.

20:52.850 --> 20:54.408
- No, no, no, no.
- Uh-uh, uh-uh, uh-uh.

20:54.450 --> 20:56.008
- What?
- Uh-uh, you are not using

20:56.050 --> 20:58.610
