going to need a healing

21:02.520 --> 21:03.680
when I steal your books.

21:03.730 --> 21:06.619
Charley, you are
Nova's partner.

21:06.660 --> 21:08.821
No, no. Rah's my partner.

21:08.860 --> 21:10.566
