21:17.770 --> 21:19.499
Come on.
Rise and fly, my love.

21:19.540 --> 21:21.303
Rise and fly.

21:21.340 --> 21:23.672
Man.

21:23.710 --> 21:26.076
Man, I'll play.
Just teach me.

21:26.110 --> 21:27.771
( all chatter)

21:27.820 --> 21:29.572
This is what you
can do right here.

21:29.620 --> 21:30.712
Baby!

21:30.750 --> 21:32.741
We love you,
but you got to go.

21:32.790 --> 21:34.417
Chuck E. Cheese
is that way,
young fella.

21:34.460 --> 21:36.018
Keep the score.
Remy, keep him honest.

21:36.060 --> 21:38.551
There's grown folks
at this table.

21:38.590 --> 21:39.784
Whoo-whee!

21:39.830 --> 21:41.354
That's what
I'm talking about

21:41.400 --> 21:42.958
Hollywood:
Big joker's the big joker.

21:43.000 --> 21:45.798
Little joker's guarantee.
First hand bid--

21:45.830 --> 21:47.366
_House_rules.
I'm just trying to say.

21:47.400 --> 21:48.867
