greater good?

28:00.140 --> 28:02.028
You know what? You...

28:03.440 --> 28:04.771
You a bougie bitch.

28:06.980 --> 28:09.448
You know that, right?

28:11.520 --> 28:13.442
I may be bougie,

28:13.490 --> 28:17.119
but at least I'm not having
an affair with a married man.

28:19.330 --> 28:22.049
I actually value marriage,

28:22.100 --> 28:23.863
even if no one else
in my life does.

28:23.900 --> 28:26.960
And I'm not gonna have
my son be stuck again
in a house

28:27.000 --> 28:29.059
where people who claim
to love one another

28:29.100 --> 28:31.409
disrespect each other
and break their promises.

28:31.440 --> 28:35.308
You want to live foul?
Okay, you do you.

28:51.230 --> 28:51.958
- ( thunder crashes )
- Pop!

28:56.530 --> 28:58.998
It's okay, Blue.

28:59.030 --> 29:01.066
I got this.
You can leave.

29:01.100 --> 29:03.830
No, Mommy, stay.

29:03.870 --> 29:05.235
It's all right, buddy.

29:05.270 --> 29:08.239
Let's count the seconds
until the thunder, okay?

29:08.280 --> 29:12.102
That's how we know
how close the storm is.

29:12.150 --> 29:14.311
Pop, will you get
in the bed?

29:16.020 --> 29:18.284
I don't know
ifI could fit, buddy.

29:20.020 --> 29:21.988
But I'll tell you what.

29:22.020 --> 29:24.056
Scoot over and I'll try.

29:24.090 --> 29:25.387
Okay.

29:25.430 --> 29:26.852
All right.

29:44.110 --> 29:47.477
You messing around
with somebody else's husband?

29:53.590 --> 29:55.148
And you're doing this

29:55.190 --> 29:59.229
with all that your
baby sister's been through?

30:00.860 --> 30:03.420
We're not together anymore,

30:03.460 --> 30:04.961
SO...

30:07.230 --> 30:08.936
this ain't the same.

30:12.370 --> 30:15.032
It ain't the same as...

30:15.080 --> 30:17.878
looking at your own mother,

30:17.910 --> 30:22.040
and everything
she went through
with Ernest...

30:22.080 --> 30:24.287
and Charley's mama?

30:28.060 --> 30:29.459
Or don't you remember
any of that?

30:29.490 --> 30:31.924
I haven't forgotten
anything.

30:42.570 --> 30:44.299
( sighs )

31:03.590 --> 31:05.524
Yeah, I miss him, too.

31:09.160 --> 31:13.062
If Ernest knew the mess

31:13.100 --> 31:16.331
you pulled with your wife,

31:18.010 --> 31:21.878
he would've run you
out of town like he did
Jimmy Dale.

31:25.080 --> 31:26.968
Vi, I know you mad at me.

31:28.680 --> 31:32.343
But how do you fix your lips
to compare me to Jimmy Dale?

31:33.490 --> 31:36.152
That man wasn't no man.
He was a coward.

31:36.190 --> 31:39.159
I would never
put my hands on you.

31:39.190 --> 31:41.624
How could you say
something like that?

31:41.660 --> 31:43.491
No, you never hit me.

31:45.400 --> 31:48.892
But you sure knocked
the hell out of me.

31:52.170 --> 31:54.377
Every word you said
was a lie.

31:54.410 --> 31:56.674
I ain't never lied
when I said I loved you.

31:56.710 --> 31:58.348
And it wasn't no lie
when I said

31:58.380 --> 31:59.699
you was the only one
for me.

31:59.750 --> 32:00.944
You know that.

32:00.980 --> 32:02.242
You sure about that?

32:02.280 --> 32:05.579
Me and Leanne was done
way before we even started.

32:05.620 --> 32:07.952
One-night stand ain't
no foundation for a marriage.

32:07.990 --> 32:09.287
( laughs )

32:09.320 --> 32:12.027
So that's supposed
to make things better?

32:12.060 --> 32:14.494
That a fling
put it on you so good

32:14.530 --> 32:16.293
you had to drop down
on one knee?

32:16.330 --> 32:17.695
It wasn't like that.

32:17.730 --> 32:20.198
I was trying to to do right
by her and that baby,

32:20.230 --> 32:22.289
so we got hitched.

32:22.340 --> 32:24.160
Then she lost the baby...

32:24.210 --> 32:26.599
and she got worse.

32:26.640 --> 32:29.177
And I was the only
shoulder she had.

32:29.210 --> 32:30.734
She has family.

32:30.780 --> 32:33.044
She got a cousin
that's a telephone operator

32:33.080 --> 32:36.470
that calls me every time
she gets off them pills.

32:39.090 --> 32:41.979
Well, it's funny that you...

32:42.020 --> 32:43.419
didn't mention any of this

32:43.460 --> 32:45.382
when you and I got going.

32:45.430 --> 32:48.593
You said you didn't want
to get married again.

32:48.630 --> 32:51.519
And me and Leanne
was way done.

32:51.570 --> 32:53.492
And I didn't risk you

32:53.530 --> 32:55.339
not wanting to start up
with me because of it,

32:55.370 --> 32:57.736
so I left the past
in the past.

33:00.070 --> 33:01.207
( scoffs )

33:01.240 --> 33:02.571
My big mama would
roll over in her grave

33:02.610 --> 33:05.545
if she saw I wasn't trying
to help anybody like that.

33:12.650 --> 33:14.413
Me and you,

33:14.460 --> 33:17.111
we ain't Jimmy Dale
and Leanne.

33:17.160 --> 33:19.526
We better than that.

33:25.530 --> 33:27.669
Are we that much better?

33:42.620 --> 33:43.143
( match scratches )

33:50.290 --> 33:51.780
Hey.

33:51.830 --> 33:53.286
Hey.

33:53.330 --> 33:54.399
He sleeping good?

33:54.430 --> 33:56.796
Better than us.

33:58.530 --> 34:02.068
You can make a pallet
in the living room to sleep on.

34:02.100 --> 34:03.692
I'll stay here with Blue.

34:05.310 --> 34:07.562
We could both stay.

34:10.840 --> 34:13.809
Violet:
Ralph Angel, come out here.

34:13.850 --> 34:15.477
( Ralph Angel sighs )

34:22.120 --> 34:23.712
Ralph Angel?

34:27.460 --> 34:28.757
Come here.

34:32.230 --> 34:33.720
( door closes )

34:43.380 --> 34:46.645
You making
a big mistake.

34:48.580 --> 34:50.775
I told you
about that girl.

34:54.920 --> 34:58.754
You letting her
right back in,
ain't you?

34:59.790 --> 35:04.227
Aunt Vi, please stay
out of something.

35:05.500 --> 35:07.229
For once.

35:08.800 --> 35:11.860
I told you about her,
and I did stay out of it.

35:11.910 --> 35:13.400
Look what happened.

35:13.440 --> 35:16.102
- Blue's what happened!
- That may be true.

35:17.380 --> 35:21.146
But can't nobody
trust that girl.

35:21.180 --> 35:23.648
After what she done
to Blue?

35:23.680 --> 35:26.114
- ( door opens
- To you? )

35:28.390 --> 35:29.709
( mumbles )

35:37.830 --> 35:40.867
I'm not my past mistakes,
Miss Violet.

35:40.900 --> 35:43.460
( sighs )

35:43.500 --> 35:46.537
These past 18 months,

35:46.570 --> 35:48.504
I've been clean.

35:49.810 --> 35:52.574
You come 18 years
from now saying that,

35:52.610 --> 35:54.271
and I'll believe it.

35:55.750 --> 35:58.685
You want me to wait
18 years

35:58.720 --> 36:00.745
before I get my son back?

36:02.490 --> 36:03.684
Get him back?

36:05.690 --> 36:08.523
If it were up to me,
you wouldn't lay eyes
on him.

36:12.830 --> 36:15.833
I want...

36:17.470 --> 36:18.903
to thank you.

36:18.940 --> 36:20.601
( sniffles )

36:22.980 --> 36:27.269
I never got the chance
to say thank you,
Miss Violet.

36:37.390 --> 36:39.858
And I want to thank you.

36:42.300 --> 36:43.949
You saw me

36:44.000 --> 36:46.560
at my lowest point.

36:48.700 --> 36:51.567
You saw me in hell.

36:54.010 --> 36:57.207
I didn't even want
to eXIst anymore.

36:58.350 --> 37:00.238
Not breathe.

37:01.880 --> 37:03.347
Not see.

37:04.890 --> 37:06.209
Not hear.

37:09.620 --> 37:11.759
Love couldn't even
reach me.

37:14.760 --> 37:17.228
And you picked up my baby.

37:19.030 --> 37:20.918
Gently.

37:27.010 --> 37:29.535
I remember.

37:29.580 --> 37:31.002
( sniffles )

37:31.040 --> 37:34.646
And I remember you
running that man out
of that motel room.

37:36.750 --> 37:39.981
And you could have
yelled at me

37:40.020 --> 37:42.284
and cursed me.

37:44.020 --> 37:47.786
But I remember you
covering me up

37:47.830 --> 37:51.891
and saying,
"God bless you, girl."

37:51.930 --> 37:53.329
( sniffles )

37:56.540 --> 37:58.735
I remember that.

38:02.040 --> 38:04.076
And when you walked out
of that door,

38:04.110 --> 38:05.839
I thought...

38:09.420 --> 38:10.842
"Thank God."

38:15.620 --> 38:18.680
"Thank God,
Blue will be okay."

38:22.060 --> 38:24.290
So, I thank you.

38:27.570 --> 38:29.663
Both of you.

38:30.900 --> 38:33.368
And I want to make amends.

38:36.610 --> 38:39.340
I want to pay back
my debts...

38:41.050 --> 38:44.315
and bring goodness to where
I brought discord.

38:47.450 --> 38:48.986
That's all I'm trying to do.

38:52.430 --> 38:53.988
And I hope...

38:58.430 --> 39:01.991
I hope that one day
you'll see fit to let me.

41:36.860 --> 41:38.054
( sighs )

42:01.210 --> 42:02.871
( sighs )

42:35.950 --> 42:38.009
( music playing )
